{
  "stem": "24397.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I, I mentioned that I really enjoyed riding bicycles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had to rent them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, the bikes-- the rental place was inside a park.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by this time, parks were already out of bounds to Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but I had been going there for a long time, so I used to go through there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On one occasion, I thought I had lost my money, and I got pretty upset.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was looking all over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I thought I'd lost it on the floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And an old fellow came over, sort of a grandpa type.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Seemed to be a nice man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he asked me what the problem was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I told him I thought I'd lost my money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he started putting his arm around me, started giving me a lecture on, little boy, Hitler wouldn't be happy if he saw me crying.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was giving me this real Nazi propaganda speech.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it so happened I found the money caught in the seam of my pocket.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so as I felt that, I brightened up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he probably thought it was due to his talk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the reason I bring it up is because people tend to think that these fanatic Nazis were all a rowdy rabble.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were these nice old guys, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so I went and got my bicycle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I came home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my dad was-- [INAUDIBLE] [CRYING] He was waiting at the window.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[CRYING] And I guess you can tell I have very strong feelings [CRYING] towards my father.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[CRYING] I'm OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was waiting at the window for you to get home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'd ride up and down, no hands, and all that kind of thing and, and take it back, and--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
